1182
01:19:37,827 --> 01:19:41,026
Faubert. Listen,
contact Dimitri Zvenka.

1183
01:19:41,187 --> 01:19:42,346
- Your coyote?
- My doctor.

1184
01:19:42,907 --> 01:19:44,186
He's known me forever.

1185
01:19:44,427 --> 01:19:46,826
He'll testify, they'll let me go.

1186
01:19:47,027 --> 01:19:49,866
