1231
01:23:11,189 --> 01:23:14,629
Romain Faubert, not Sergei!
I don't know him.

1232
01:23:19,750 --> 01:23:21,229
Let me go.

1233
01:23:21,910 --> 01:23:23,668
I'm a French hypochondriac.

1234
01:23:23,830 --> 01:23:25,468
